description: Master supply view containing datacenter attributes such as provider, rentable space, raised floor space, power utilization, location info, ownership details, operational status, and region mappings.
calculatedmetrics: TotalDeployed; AvailableDeployed; UnderConstructionPower; Land; LiveRaisedSpace; VacantRaisedSpace; LiveInventory; VacantInventory

description: Quarter-over-quarter power supply metrics including total deployed power, available power, under construction power, land power and their respective percentages.
calculatedmetrics: TotalDeployedQoQ; UnderConstructionPowerQoQ; AvailableDeployedQoQ; LandpowerQoQ; TotalDeployedQoQPercentage; UnderConstructionPowerQoQPercentage; AvailableDeployedQoQPercentage; LandpowerQoQPercentage

description: Quarter-over-quarter demand-side DLR metrics including live inventory, vacant inventory, raised floor space, and their percentage changes.
calculatedmetrics: QOQ_LiveInventory; QOQ_VacantInventory; QOQ_LiveRaisedSpace; QOQ_VacantRaisedSpace; QOQ_per_LiveInventory; QOQ_per_VacantInventory; QOQ_per_LiveRaisedSpace; QOQ_per_VacantRaisedSpace
